# API Reference for cdktf.IResolvable

   IResolvable <a name="IResolvable" id="cdktf.IResolvable"></a>
  
  - *Implemented By:* <a href="#cdktf.AnyMap">AnyMap</a>, <a href="#cdktf.AnyMapList">AnyMapList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.BooleanMap">BooleanMap</a>, <a href="#cdktf.BooleanMapList">BooleanMapList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.ComplexComputedList">ComplexComputedList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.ComplexList">ComplexList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.ComplexMap">ComplexMap</a>, <a href="#cdktf.ComplexObject">ComplexObject</a>, <a href="#cdktf.LazyBase">LazyBase</a>, <a href="#cdktf.NumberMap">NumberMap</a>, <a href="#cdktf.NumberMapList">NumberMapList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.StringMap">StringMap</a>, <a href="#cdktf.StringMapList">StringMapList</a>, <a href="#cdktf.IResolvable">IResolvable</a>
  
  Interface for values that can be resolvable later.
  
  Tokens are special objects that participate in synthesis.

  ## `creationStack`<sup>Required</sup> <a name="creationStack" id="cdktf.IResolvable.property.creationStack"></a>
  
  ```typescript
  public readonly creationStack: string[];
  ```
  
  - *Type:* string[]
  
  The creation stack of this resolvable which will be appended to errors thrown during resolution.
  
  If this returns an empty array the stack will not be attached.
